import * as React from 'react';
import { CssBaseline, Link, Avatar, TextField, Typography, Paper, Box, Grid, Button, Checkbox, FormControlLabel, Container, Card } from '@material-ui/core';


import PhoneLocked from '@material-ui/icons/ScreenLockLandscape';
import useStyles from './styles';


const Auth = () => {
    const classes = useStyles();

    return (
        <Container>
            <Card className={classes.card} >
                <Box className={classes.container}>
                    <Box className={classes.avatar}><Avatar sx={{ bgcolor: Pink[500] }}><PhoneLocked /></Avatar> Sign In </Box>
                    <form >
                        <Box className={classes.form} >    <TextField

                            name="email"
                            required
                            id="email"
                            label="Email"
                            variant="filled"
                            onChange=''
                            fullWidth
                        />
                            <TextField

                                name="password"
                                required
                                id="password"
                                label="Password"
                                variant="filled"
                                type="password"
                                onChange=''
                                fullWidth
                            />

                        </Box>
                        <Box className={classes.button}>
                            <Button variant="contained" color="secondary" size="large" type="submit"  > Log In</Button>
                        </Box>
                    </form>
                </Box>
            </Card>



        </Container >

    );
}
export default Auth;
